              "free_text": [
                " Systematic error."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 4He  photodisintegration  cross  section  has been",
                " measured in the energy region from 20 to 32  MeV.  In",
                " the measurement  a  laser-Compton-backscattered-gamma",
                " beam and a time projection chamber were employed. The",
                " result indicates the cross section increases up to 32",
                " MeV, and there is no pronounced peak at around 25 MeV",
                " which has been previously adopted as the giant dipole",
                " resonance energy.",
                "In addition, the data of the total photoabsorption",
                " cross section of 12C were used in order to check the",
                " overall sensitivity of the measurement, including the",
                " determination of the incident g-ray flux."
              ]
            }
          ],
